{"type":"message","id":"154c336c","parentId":"df49b6ca","timestamp":"2026-03-05T05:13:11.305Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-03-05 13:13 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 你好，元栈！我是纬策。\n\n青峰需要一个**实时数据可视化方案**，请帮我评估技术可行性：\n\n1. 实时数据可视化的主流技术栈有哪些？\n2. 各方案的优缺点和适用场景是什么？\n3. 实施复杂度如何？\n4. 有什么技术风险需要注意？\n\n请提供技术层面的分析和建议，我会据此设计解决方案。"}],"timestamp":1772687591303}}
{"type":"message","id":"52701550","parentId":"154c336c","timestamp":"2026-03-05T05:13:19.036Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我是作为元栈（技术评估专家）被纬策委派了一个任务：评估实时数据可视化方案的技术可行性。\n\n任务很明确：\n1. 主流技术栈有哪些\n2. 各方案的优缺点和适用场景\n3. 实施复杂度\n4. 技术风险\n\n让我先搜索一下当前实时数据可视化的主流技术栈和最佳实践，然后给出专业的技术评估。\n\n我需要：\n1. 使用 web_search 搜索实时数据可视化技术栈\n2. 整理分析各种方案的优劣\n3. 给出技术层面的建议\n\n让我开始搜索。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来帮你评估实时数据可视化的技术方案。先搜索一下当前主流的技术栈和最佳实践。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-ad19cf5c9af84a3e8a8adf1834e0adf8","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"query":"real-time data visualization technology stack 2024 2025 best practices"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-63832dd9ad8d40cc91164740daa4134a","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"query":"WebSocket Server-Sent Events SSE real-time dashboard comparison"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-f00afabf47144bff8ce9835d98cb2062","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"query":"Apache Kafka real-time streaming visualization architecture"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2276,"output":347,"cacheRead":4357,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":6980,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772687591305}}
{"type":"message","id":"fefbe709","parentId":"52701550","timestamp":"2026-03-05T05:13:19.053Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-ad19cf5c9af84a3e8a8adf1834e0adf8","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_kimi_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search (kimi) needs a Moonshot API key. Set KIMI_API_KEY or MOONSHOT_API_KEY in the Gateway environment, or configure tools.web.search.kimi.apiKey.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_kimi_api_key","message":"web_search (kimi) needs a Moonshot API key. Set KIMI_API_KEY or MOONSHOT_API_KEY in the Gateway environment, or configure tools.web.search.kimi.apiKey.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772687599051}}
